entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You have recovered all the data from the uppermost level of this place. Head downstairs to the main research floor.
entries.journal_entry_description: Data is missing from the administrative computers. Get data from the administrative heads, no matter the cost.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Benn Calder is one of the administrative heads. Kill him and get into his computer.
entries.task00_journal_entry_title: Kill Benn Calder to get his Passcode
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Ben Calder's computer likely has some of the missing information that Lt. Joth needs. With his passcode, break into the computer and download the data.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Pirt Rawklin is the second administrative head. Kill him and get into his computer.
entries.task02_journal_entry_title: Kill Pirt Rawklin to get his Passcode
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Pirt Rawklin's computer likely has some of the missing information that Lt. Joth needs. With his passcode, break into the computer and download the data.
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Rond Fenimer is the final administrative head. Kill him and get into his computer.
entries.task04_journal_entry_title: Kill Rond Fenimer to get his Passcode
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: Rond Fenimer's computer likely has the rest of the missing information that Lt. Joth needs. With his passcode, break into the computer and download the data.
entries.task06_comm_message_text: It's a lab, all right. It's being used to bio-engineer creatures. This may be sanctioned for some labs, but this one is operating under the radar. This means trouble. Shut the place down.
entries.task06_journal_entry_description: You received a message from Lt. Joth: It's a lab, all right. It's being used to bio-engineer creatures. This may be sanctioned for some labs, but this one is operating under the radar. This means trouble. Shut the place down.
